    <item>
      <title>Catalog</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/catalog/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Aug 2022 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/catalog/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Catalog module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you to showcase your bookable resources. Alongside, it also allows to create custom categories of items (services, etc&amp;hellip;) to show.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;As for resources, &lt;em&gt;Antibodies module&lt;/em&gt; is automatically bindable to the &lt;em&gt;Catalog module&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../catalog_module_2.png&#34; alt=&#34;catalog_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#resources-showcase&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Resources showcase&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#custom-items&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Custom items&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#antibodies-showcase&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Antibodies showcase&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Module activation and configuration&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/catalog/#module-activation-and-configuration&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Module activation and configuration&#34; href=&#34;#module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Within your space, go into &lt;em&gt;Configuration&lt;/em&gt; module.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Com</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/com/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Aug 2022 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/com/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Com module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you to display informational messages news on your home page.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../com_module_5.png&#34; alt=&#34;com_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#space-tile-message&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Display a message on your home page&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#news&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Edit news and program their display&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Module activation and configuration&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/com/#module-activation-and-configuration&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Module activation and configuration&#34; href=&#34;#module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Within your space, go into &lt;em&gt;Com&lt;/em&gt; module. Com module could be found on the second page.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../basic_configuration_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;basic configuration&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Then click edit button in &lt;em&gt;com&lt;/em&gt; line.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Invoices</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/invoices/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Aug 2022 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/invoices/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Invoices module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you to create and send invoices related bookings, orders and projects.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../invoices_module_5.png&#34; alt=&#34;invoices_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#booking-invoices&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;generate booking invoices&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#project-invoices&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;generate project invoices&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#order-invoices&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;generate order invoices&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#global-invoices&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;generate global invoices&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#defining-prices&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;define prices&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Module activation and configuration&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/invoices/#module-activation-and-configuration&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Module activation and configuration&#34; href=&#34;#module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Within your space, go into &lt;em&gt;Configuration&lt;/em&gt; module.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../basic_configuration_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;basic configuration&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Then click edit button in &lt;em&gt;invoices&lt;/em&gt; line.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can now select the minimum role required to access the module. &amp;ldquo;Inactive&amp;rdquo; option stands for &amp;ldquo;the module is not active&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Mailer</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/mailer/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Aug 2022 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/mailer/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mailer module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you email your space users according to filters on role or resources used.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../mailer_module_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;mailer_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Module activation and configuration&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/mailer/#module-activation-and-configuration&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Module activation and configuration&#34; href=&#34;#module-activation-and-configuration&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Within your space, go into &lt;em&gt;Configuration&lt;/em&gt; module.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../basic_configuration_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;basic configuration&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Then click edit button in &lt;em&gt;mailer&lt;/em&gt; line.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can now select the minimum role required to access the module. &amp;ldquo;Inactive&amp;rdquo; option stands for &amp;ldquo;the module is not active&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Services</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/services/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Aug 2022 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/services/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Services module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you to create &lt;strong&gt;projects&lt;/strong&gt;, &lt;strong&gt;services&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;orders&lt;/strong&gt; as well as managing &lt;strong&gt;stocks&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../services_module_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;resources_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#manage-projects&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;projects&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#manage-orders&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;orders&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#creating-a-service&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;services&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#manage-stocks&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;stocks&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Item definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/services/#item-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Item definition&#34; href=&#34;#item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;project&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Project&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/services/#project&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Project&#34; href=&#34;#project&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Provides project following using kanban board, gantt diagram.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Invoicable items - &lt;em&gt;services&lt;/em&gt; - can be added to a project to have a track of what you&amp;rsquo;ll have to invoice to your clients.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Rating</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/rating/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jun 2022 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/rating/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rating module&lt;/strong&gt; allows &lt;em&gt;managers&lt;/em&gt; to create satisfaction campaigns&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;campaigns&#34;&gt;&#xA;        campaigns&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/rating/#campaigns&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor campaigns&#34; href=&#34;#campaigns&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Managers can create some satisfaction campaigns with a deadline date.&#xA;A campaign could be annual or bi-annuel for example.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Users with bookings or projects during the campaign period&#xA;receive an email with a link to rate their equipments usage or projects.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;User rate equipements and projects with a note (1 to 5) and an optional comment.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Booking</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/booking/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/booking/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Booking module&lt;/strong&gt; allows &lt;em&gt;users&lt;/em&gt; book &lt;em&gt;resources&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../booking_module_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;booking_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Unlike other modules, Booking module has the particularity to be divided into two modules: &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;#booking-module&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Booking&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;#booking-settings-module&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Booking settings&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&#xA;You will need to activate both in order set your resources reservation environment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Item definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/booking/#item-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Item definition&#34; href=&#34;#item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A reservation is defined by its:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;../resources/#item-definition&#34;&gt;Resource&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;../users/#item-definition&#34;&gt;User&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;../clients/#item-definition&#34;&gt;Client account&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Short description&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Full description&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;#color-code&#34;&gt;Color code&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;(optional) &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;#additional-info&#34;&gt;Additional infos&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;All day, i.e. does this reservation takes all day?&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Beginning (date + time)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;End (date + time)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;(optional) Periodicity&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;related-items-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Related items definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/booking/#related-items-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Related items definition&#34; href=&#34;#related-items-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;color-code&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Color code&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/booking/#color-code&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Color code&#34; href=&#34;#color-code&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;additional-info&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Additional info&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/booking/#additional-info&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Additional info&#34; href=&#34;#additional-info&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h4 id=&#34;supplementaries-info&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Supplementaries info&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/booking/#supplementaries-info&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Supplementaries info&#34; href=&#34;#supplementaries-info&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h4&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;For information on reservation. Can be set as mandatory.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Clients</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/clients/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/clients/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Clients module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you to create invoicable entities.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../clients_module_8.png&#34; alt=&#34;clients_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#add-a-client&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;clients&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#add-a-pricing&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;pricings&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#link-users-to-a-client&#34;&gt;link &lt;em&gt;users&lt;/em&gt; to a &lt;em&gt;client&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Item definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/clients/#item-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Item definition&#34; href=&#34;#item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;client&lt;/strong&gt; is the entity which can be invoiced. Users can be attached to a client, so they can book resources or ask for services in name of the &lt;em&gt;client&lt;/em&gt;. A user can&amp;rsquo;t be invoiced directly.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Documents</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/documents/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/documents/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Documents&lt;/strong&gt; module gives access to a basic documentation storage.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In the base plan, module allows space managers to upload/download&#xA;documents on a private basis only (limited to space managers).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;A document name can use a path like naming to simulate a directory&#xA;hierarchy.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Example, with a document named &lt;em&gt;resource1/usage.pdf&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;usage.pdf&lt;/em&gt; will&#xA;be displayed in &lt;em&gt;resource1&lt;/em&gt; directory. Modifying document name will&#xA;update its location accordingly. This path is virtual, ie is used for&#xA;display only and ease document categorization.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Helpdesk</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/helpdesk/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/helpdesk/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;helpdesk-for-spaces&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Helpdesk for spaces&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/helpdesk/#helpdesk-for-spaces&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Helpdesk for spaces&#34; href=&#34;#helpdesk-for-spaces&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A lightweight helpdesk system to manage tickets from users to a space.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If pfm is configured with an imap account, let&amp;rsquo;s say &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;mailto:support@pfm.org&#34;&gt;support@pfm.org&lt;/a&gt;, then&#xA;space members can send emails to &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;mailto:support&amp;#43;spaceshortname@pfm.org&#34;&gt;support+spaceshortname@pfm.org&lt;/a&gt; to create a&#xA;ticket.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Managers can see and reply to all tickets, and ease the follow-ups of users issues,&#xA;with the full conversation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Space email address is show in helpdesk configuration panel when activated.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Quote</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/quote/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/quote/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Quote module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you to create quotes.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../quote_module_1.png&#34; alt=&#34;clients_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#create-a-quote&#34;&gt;Create &lt;em&gt;quotes&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#edit-quote&#34;&gt;Edit &lt;em&gt;quotes&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Item definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/quote/#item-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Item definition&#34; href=&#34;#item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;em&gt;quote&lt;/em&gt; is defined by its (&amp;quot;*&amp;quot; for &lt;em&gt;mandatory&lt;/em&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#recipient&#34;&gt;Recipient or User*&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Recipient Email&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Client Address&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#client&#34;&gt;Client*&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;A list of &lt;em&gt;items&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;related-items-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Related items definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/quote/#related-items-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Related items definition&#34; href=&#34;#related-items-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;recipient-or-user&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Recipient or User&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/quote/#recipient-or-user&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Recipient or User&#34; href=&#34;#recipient-or-user&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;recipient&lt;/strong&gt; or &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;../users&#34;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;user&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; is the person whose name will appear in the quote header.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Resources</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/resources/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/resources/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Resources module&lt;/strong&gt; allows you to create resources that users can book.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../resources_module_6.png&#34; alt=&#34;resources_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#add-a-resource&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;resources&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#add-an-area&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;areas&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#add-a-category&#34;&gt;manage &lt;em&gt;categories&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;manage responsibles and &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#add-a-visa&#34;&gt;visas&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;manage resources states and events&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Item definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/resources/#item-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Item definition&#34; href=&#34;#item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;resource&lt;/strong&gt; is a bookable item.&#xA;It is defined by its (&amp;quot;*&amp;quot; for &lt;em&gt;mandatory&lt;/em&gt;):&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;name*&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#category&#34;&gt;category*&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#area&#34;&gt;area*&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;brand&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;type&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;display order&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;description&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;full description&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;image&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;related-items-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Related items definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/resources/#related-items-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Related items definition&#34; href=&#34;#related-items-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h3 id=&#34;category&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Category&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/resources/#category&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Category&#34; href=&#34;#category&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;category&lt;/strong&gt; contains multiple resources. For example, if you have 3 scanners (&lt;em&gt;scanner1&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;scanner2&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;scanner3&lt;/em&gt;), they can be grouped under the category &lt;em&gt;Scanners&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Statistics</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/statistics/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/statistics/</guid>
      <description>&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;statistics-dashboard&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Statistics dashboard&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/statistics/#statistics-dashboard&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Statistics dashboard&#34; href=&#34;#statistics-dashboard&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;In space page, there is a link to the statistics dashboard, for managers only.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Managers can log in dashboard with their identifier and their API Key&#xA;(in user informations panel /usersmyaccount).&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The &lt;em&gt;statistics dashboard&lt;/em&gt; is based on &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;https://grafana.com/docs/&#34;&gt;Grafana&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;and several dashboards are set by default. Additional dashboards can be created&#xA;by managers.&#xA;It is advised not to modify provided dashboards as they may be overwritten on future&#xA;updates.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Users</title>
      <link>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/users/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 13 Aug 2021 13:30:30 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/users/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Users module&lt;/strong&gt; allows space admins to manage &lt;em&gt;users&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;../../../create_user_9.png&#34; alt=&#34;users_module&#34;  /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Within this module, you can:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#users-management&#34;&gt;add &lt;em&gt;users&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#users-management&#34;&gt;authorize &lt;em&gt;users&lt;/em&gt; to access your &lt;em&gt;space&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#users-management&#34;&gt;affect roles to users within your &lt;em&gt;space&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#manage-users-booking-access&#34;&gt;manage users &lt;em&gt;booking access&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#link-clients-to-a-user&#34;&gt;manage users &lt;em&gt;client accounts&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;div class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchorwrap&#34;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;h2 id=&#34;item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;        Item definition&#xA;        &lt;a data-clipboard-text=&#34;https://bgo-bioimagerie.github.io/platformmanager/modules/module/users/#item-definition&#34; class=&#34;gdoc-page__anchor gdoc-page__anchor--right clip&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor Item definition&#34; href=&#34;#item-definition&#34;&gt;&#xA;            &lt;svg class=&#34;icon gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;use xlink:href=&#34;#gdoc_link&#34;&gt;&lt;/use&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;A &lt;strong&gt;user&lt;/strong&gt; is linked to an account. Within a space, it can be attributed different &lt;a class=&#34;gdoc-markdown__link&#34; href=&#34;./#user-space-roles&#34;&gt;&lt;em&gt;roles&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; , like &lt;em&gt;admin&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;manager&lt;/em&gt;, &lt;em&gt;user&lt;/em&gt; or &lt;em&gt;visitor&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
    </item>
  </channel>
